findings.title: Owner can make giveaway
findings.description: The owner has privileges to make a giveaway.

findings.title: Owner can change tierMintFees
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify tierMintFees, which could potentially lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change whitelistMintFee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the whitelist mint fee.

findings.title: Owner Privilege: Modification of Critical Timings
findings.description: The owner has the ability to change tierStartMintTimes, tierMintEndTimes, and whitelistSaleDisableTime, which can lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change revealTime
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to change the revealTime variable.

findings.title: Owner can withdraw contract ETHs
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to withdraw contract ETHs without any restrictions.
